OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FAnalysis by an independent climate
OL,7,Fwatchdog suggests the government is
OL,8,Fnot on track to reach crucial tree
OL,9,Fplanting targets. ITV News Science
OL,10,FCorrespondent Martin Stew reports
OL,12,FWords by Senior Science Producer
OL,13,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,15,FThe Energy and Climate Intelligence
OL,16,FUnit (ECIU) has warned the UK is
OL,17,Ffalling behind on tree planting
OL,18,Ftargets essential for meeting the
OL,19,Fcountry's environmental and carbon
OL,20,Fcapture targets by 2050.
