OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FThe government has committed to
OL,7,Fplanting 210,000 new hectares of tree
OL,8,Fcover across England by 2050 as part
OL,9,Fof its Environmental Improvement Plan.
OL,11,FThe trees will have a key role in
OL,12,Fremoving carbon from the atmosphere,
OL,13,Fimproving flood defences and helping
OL,14,Fto grow wildlife habitats.
