OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FThe ECIU analysis warns that the
OL,7,Fgovernment cannot afford to fall
OL,8,Fbehind on these planting targets if it
OL,9,Fhopes to still meet the goals set for
OL,10,F2050.
OL,12,FThe analysis found that higher
OL,13,Fplanting rates in the future cannot
OL,14,Fcompensate for missed planting now due
OL,15,Fto the time lag before trees mature
OL,16,Fenough to deliver maximum benefits for
OL,17,Fcarbon removal, biodiversity and flood
OL,18,Frisk prevention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
