OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FMature trees are also beneficial in
OL,7,Fprotecting homes against the risk of
OL,8,Fflooding by slowing the flow of water
OL,9,Fduring downpours, something that
OL,10,Fjuvenile trees are not as effective at.
OL,12,FClimate change projections show 1.7
OL,13,Fmillion more homes will be at risk of
OL,14,Fflooding by 2050.
OL,16,FTom Cantillon, a senior analyst at the
OL,17,FECIU said: "Trees sucking carbon out
OL,18,Fof the atmosphere are critical to the
OL,19,FUK reaching net zero - the only way
OL,20,Fthe world can stop climate change and
OL,21,Fbring our climate back into balance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
