OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,F"After years of delay and missed
OL,7,Ftargets, trees need to be planted now
OL,8,Fif they are to grow to maturity in
OL,9,Ftime to absorb carbon emissions to
OL,10,Fhelp hit targets and also to slow the
OL,11,Fflow of the extreme rainfall that is
OL,12,Fgetting worse in the UK because of
OL,13,Fclimate change.
OL,15,F"The public are all for restoring
OL,16,FBritish nature and more trees.
OL,17,FGovernment now need to step up,
OL,18,Fdelivering the kind of woodland
OL,19,Fcreation we've seen in the past but
OL,20,Fhaven't for a few decades."
